Use the standard library
This is how to triples_sum_to_zero of l:
   Remember that n is l's length
   Remember that count is 0
   Remember that i is 0
   Do this n times:
      Remember that j is sum of i and 1
      Remember that nj is diff of n and j
      Do this nj times:
         Remember that k is sum of j and 1
         Remember that nk is diff of n and k
         Do this nk times:
            Remember that total is sum of item i in l and (sum of item j in l and item k in l)
            When total is 0, then:
               Increase count
            End when
            Increase k
         End do
         Increase j
      End do
      Increase i
   End do
   The answer is count
Now you know
>>> triples_sum_to_zero of [1, 3, 5, 0] 
0
>>> triples_sum_to_zero of [1, 3, -2, 1] 
1
>>> triples_sum_to_zero of [1, 2, 3, 7] 
0